SD.16 StructureDefinition-practitioner-qualification

An extension to add additional elements about a practitioner’s qualifications.

Consists of: * qualification.status - indicates the current status of the qualification * qualification.whereValid - indicates where the qualification is valid * qualification.history - describes the history of the qualification through changes in the status of the qualification, e.g. if the qualification was ever revoked or suspended
